divs: Sighting Detailstriangle with three white lights at the points, with one red light in the middle. Was at treetop level, saw it slow very slowly across and over the houses in the subdivision. There was a low dull sound, but barely able to hear it. Few minutes later, I looked out the 2nd story window and I saw three very bright lights in the distance in the sky. These were not moving but very bright. The You Tube video of the O Fallon UFO sighting is exactly what I saw in the sky.
